query: CREATE TABLE default.fact_rt_local UUID '55c9ee8e-f2dd-466d-a789-848a41635720' (`subscriber_key` String, `start_time` DateTime, `end_time` DateTime, `int_ipv4` IPv4, `ext_ipv4` IPv4, `app_key` LowCardinality(String), `uli` String, `request_host` String, `volume_in` UInt64, `volume_out` UInt64, `conndr_record_type` UInt8, `IMEITAC` Int64, `IMSI` Int64, `IMEISV` Int64, `sg_name` LowCardinality(String)) ENGINE = MergeTree PARTITION BY toStartOfHour(start_time) ORDER BY (start_time, app_key) TTL start_time + toIntervalHour(12) SETTINGS index_granularity = 8192
